&lt;li&gt;Serve as a strategic consultant by working closely with customers to discover their business needs, leading design workshops, and coaching them on how to best use Brex to solve their challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive customer success and adoption by developing strategies to ramp up spending activity, and providing global change management planning to guide clients on their communication approach, training materials, and execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and cultivate customer relationships by building multi-threaded connections from senior leaders to day-to-day stakeholders, managing expectations, and working diligently to provide solutions to any challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a key cross-functional partner within the Brex account team, collaborating with Sales, Customer Success, and Partnerships to deliver a smooth customer experience and align on partner-led solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence product development by adapting quickly to product changes, communicating them strategically to stakeholders, and providing a key voice into future iterations of the product roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and execute a prioritization strategy for managing multiple high-touch customer relationships effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
